tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE UserActivities (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    activity_description STRING
)

CREATE TABLE LoginEvents (
    event_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    login_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    ip_address INET,
    device_info STRING
)

CREATE TABLE DeviceTracking (
    device_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    last_activity TIMESTAMP,
    location STRING
)

CREATE TABLE SuspiciousActivities (
    activity_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    activity_description STRING
)

CREATE TABLE AuthenticationLogs (
    log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    status STRING
)
